[0.0,"o","\u001b[1mClaude Code, two hours into a session:\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[1.0,"o","  Long sessions drift.\r\n"]
[2.0,"o","  Your CLAUDE.md gets ignored.\r\n"]
[3.0,"o","  /compact wipes your instructions.\r\n"]
[4.0,"o","  Padded answers. Faked results. Surprise deletions.\r\n"]
